{"bio":null,"bio_l":"和傀儡以及石像鬼类似，撼地者也曾经是大地的一部分，但现在他自由地行走在地面上。不同于那些存在，撼地者自身的意志创造了他，他不需要服从于任何主人。在岩石深处不安宁的沉睡中，他感到了上方世界自由自在的生命的存在。他对此产生了好奇心。在一个地震多发的时期，尼西埃雪山摇动的山顶发生了雪崩，河流的流径改变了，浅浅的山谷变成了深不可测的深渊。大地停止震动后，撼地者从沉淀的灰土中走了出来，像脱下毯子一样抖落无数岩石。他幻化成他想象中的野兽的外形，并自称雷格石蹄。他现在流动着血液、呼吸着空气、也会死亡。但他的精神仍然与大地同在，他的力量在那根永不离身的魔力图腾中。当他回归尘土的那天，大地仍会欢迎这个浪子回家。","stats":"<img src=\"Int\" alt=\"Intelligence\" />Intelligence:16 + 1.80<br /><img src=\"Agi\" alt=\"Agility\" />Agility:12 + 1.40<br /><img src=\"Str\" alt=\"Strength\" />Strength:22 + 2.90<br /><img src=\"Attack\" alt=\"Damage\" />Damage:24 - 34<br /><img src=\"Speed\" alt=\"Movespeed\" />Movespeed:310<br /><img src=\"Defense\" alt=\"Armor\" />Armor:2.68","stats1":[["Int","Intelligence","16 + 1.80"],["Agi","Agility","12 + 1.40"],["Str","Strength","22 + 2.90"],["Attack","Damage","24 - 34"],["Speed","Movespeed","310"],["Defense","Armor","2.68"]],"detailstats":"<div class=\"redboxContent\"><div class=\"redboxTop\"></div><div id=\"statsInner\"><div id=\"statsLeft\"><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowCol\">25</div><div class=\"statRowCol\">15</div><div class=\"statRowCol\">1</div>等级</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">2,270</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">1,339</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">568</div>生命值</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">1,030</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">536</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">208</div>魔法值</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">136-146</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">87-97</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">46-56</div>攻击力</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">10</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">5</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">3</div>护甲</div></div><div id=\"statsRight\"><div class=\"statRow\"></div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">1800 / 800</div>视野范围</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">128</div>攻击范围</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">N/A</div>弹道速度</div></div><br clear=\"both\" /></div><div class=\"redboxBottom\"></div></div>","detailstats1":[["生命值","2,270","1,339","568"],["魔法值","1,030","536","208"],["攻击力","136-146","87-97","46-56"],["护甲","10","5","3"]],"detailstats2":[["视野范围","1800 / 800"],["攻击范围","128"],["弹道速度","N/A"]],"abilities":[{"key_name":"earthshaker_fissure","dname":"沟壑","affects":"技能：<span class=\"attribVal\">点目标</span><br />影响：<span class=\"attribVal\">敌方单位</span><br />伤害类型：<span class=\"attribVal\">魔法</span><br />无视技能免疫：<span class=\"attribVal\">否</span>","desc":"用威武的图腾猛击地面，沿直线裂开地面，制造一条无法通过的岩脊。同时眩晕和伤害敌方单位。","dmg":"攻击力:<span class=\"attribVal\">125 / 175 / 225 / 275</span>","notes":"小兵将会等待沟壑消失，不会去尝试绕开它。<br />沟壑不会被林肯法球抵挡。","attrib":"沟壑距离： <span class=\"attribVal\">1400</span><br />\n沟壑持续时间： <span class=\"attribVal\">8</span><br />\n眩晕时间： <span class=\"attribVal\">1 / 1.25 / 1.5 / 1.75</span>","cmb":"<img src=\"mana\" alt=\"魔法消耗\" />魔法消耗:125/140/155/170<br /><img src=\"cooldown\" alt=\"冷却时间\" />冷却时间:15","lore":"尼西埃图腾能以惊世之力使大地裂开。","hurl":"Earthshaker"},{"key_name":"earthshaker_enchant_totem","dname":"强化图腾","affects":"技能：<span class=\"attribVal\">无目标</span>","desc":"增强撼地者的图腾，下次攻击造成额外伤害。","dmg":"攻击力:<span class=\"attribVal\">0 / 0 / 0 / 0</span>","notes":"攻击力加成是基于基础攻击力和主属性数值。","attrib":"攻击力提升： <span class=\"attribVal\">100% / 200% / 300% / 400%</span><br />\n持续时间： <span class=\"attribVal\">14 / 14 / 14 / 14</span>","cmb":"<img src=\"mana\" alt=\"魔法消耗\" />魔法消耗:20/30/40/50<br /><img src=\"cooldown\" alt=\"冷却时间\" />冷却时间:5","lore":"瑞格勇猛的的蛮力能摧毁山脉。","hurl":"Earthshaker"},{"key_name":"earthshaker_aftershock","dname":"余震","affects":"技能：<span class=\"attribVal\">被动</span><br />伤害类型：<span class=\"attribVal\">魔法</span><br />无视技能免疫：<span class=\"attribVal\">否</span>","desc":"撼地者施放技能时会引起脚下的大地震动，眩晕附近的敌方单位并造成额外伤害。","dmg":"攻击力:<span class=\"attribVal\">50 / 75 / 100 / 125</span>","notes":"使用物品不会触发余震。","attrib":"作用范围： <span class=\"attribVal\">300</span><br />\n持续时间： <span class=\"attribVal\">0.6 / 0.9 / 1.2 / 1.5</span>","cmb":"","lore":"大地在瑞格强有力的步伐下颤抖。","hurl":"Earthshaker"},{"key_name":"earthshaker_echo_slam","dname":"回音击","affects":"技能：<span class=\"attribVal\">无目标</span><br />伤害类型：<span class=\"attribVal\">魔法</span><br />无视技能免疫：<span class=\"attribVal\">否</span>","desc":"穿过地面的冲击波，伤害敌方单位。每个受到攻击的敌人都会引起伤害附近单位的反射波。\r\n\r\n可用神杖升级。","dmg":"攻击力:<span class=\"attribVal\">160 / 210 / 270</span>","notes":"不会伤害如处于幽魂形态下的虚无单位。<br />产生回音的单位也会受到他们生成的声波造成的伤害。","attrib":"作用范围： <span class=\"attribVal\">575</span><br />\n回音伤害： <span class=\"attribVal\">40 / 55 / 70</span>","cmb":"<img src=\"mana\" alt=\"魔法消耗\" />魔法消耗:145/205/265<br /><img src=\"cooldown\" alt=\"冷却时间\" />冷却时间:150/130/110","lore":"地壳开裂，山岳折叠，回音击压碎敌人。","hurl":"Earthshaker"}],"itembuilds":{"Starting":["clarity","clarity","clarity","tango","flask","gauntlets","branches"],"Early":["magic_stick","boots","bracer","energy_booster"],"Core":["magic_wand","arcane_boots","blink","tpscroll"],"Luxury":["ultimate_scepter","veil_of_discord","shivas_guard","sheepstick","heart","octarine_core"]},"skillup":[{"groupName":"常规技能加点方式","desc":"<p>1.沟堑作为ES的核心技能，集AOE，超远距离控制，封路/分割战场于一身的神技，作为主力技能很实用。<br />2.以余震这个被动技能为第二技能，高等级的余震AOE眩晕时间会更长。<br />3.4级时升一级强化图腾，主要用途是来触发一次余震，但目前来说神牛一般在拥有2级的余震后才会加E技能，因为2级余震配合F可以直接杀掉远程兵，而牛前期缺魔法，50魔法的E很少有机会用，一般魔法豆会留给F技能，后面3级可根据玩家自己的喜好决定什么时候加，黄点优先或者图腾优先都是可行的。优先黄点，三围更高；优先图腾，爆发力更强。<br />4.回音击是老牛的主力高爆发AOE技能，几乎可以认为是没有伤害上限的。需要特别注意的是回音击的初始伤害是物理伤害，弹射伤害为魔法伤害，如果骨法给自己虚无了，或者绿杖开启，神牛的C在没有兵弹射的情况下是无法对英雄造成伤害的。</p>","abilityKeys":["earthshaker_fissure","earthshaker_aftershock","earthshaker_fissure","earthshaker_enchant_totem","earthshaker_fissure","earthshaker_echo_slam","earthshaker_fissure","earthshaker_aftershock","earthshaker_aftershock","earthshaker_aftershock","earthshaker_echo_slam","earthshaker_enchant_totem","earthshaker_enchant_totem","earthshaker_enchant_totem","attribute_bonus","earthshaker_echo_slam","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus","attribute_bonus"]},{"grou